1. Jarvis initializes TTS engine and loads Gemini configuration.
2. Greets the user depending on the current time.
3. Listens for commands via microphone.
4. Processes the command to determine intent.
5. Executes the corresponding function (open app, close app, shutdown, etc.).
6. Logs the command into command_history.json.
7. Provides response through speech.
8. Repeats the loop until user exits.
